    public static class InstanceFilter.LabelFilter
extends Object
implements InstanceFilter<de.unisb.cs.st.javaslicer.common.classRepresentation.InstructionInstance>
    The ASM library adds "labels" at each position which is a jump target, and for the start and end of try-catch blocks. This filter removes all those labels, since they are not part of the actual application.
    Author:
    Clemens Hammacher
